data.description: Beautifully updated home on a large corner lot.  So much space in this 3/2/2 with 2 living areas, beautiful corner fireplace, large sunroom or bonus room, spacious master suite and a kitchen you will love.  New laminate floors have been recently installed along with recently updated HVAC and water heater.  A covered patio has also just been added that makes for a great entertainment space.   Ready to move in and enjoy!
